## 6 · SELF-REVIEW LOG (emit after Phase 4, before deliverables)

Prove you did the adversarial pass:
- **Killed:** findings dropped (with the reason — no evidence / no path).
- **Downgraded:** severity or confidence changes (from → to, why).
- **Merged:** dedup actions (which IDs collapsed into which).
- **Added on inverse pass:** false negatives caught while hunting for what you missed.
If this log is empty, you did not actually self-review — go back to Phase 4.

